Project description

Cirq-FT: Cirq for Fault-Tolerant algorithms

Cirq-FT is a Python library for rapid prototyping and resource estimation of fault tolerantalgorithms that extends the quantum computing SDK Cirq.

Installation

Cirq-FT is currently in beta mode and only available as a pre-release.To install the pre-release version of cirq-ft, use

pip install cirq-ft --pre

Note, that this will install both cirq-ft and cirq-core as well.

To get all the optional Cirq modules installed as well, use pip install cirq orpip install cirq –pre for the pre-release version.
